Hannah Waterman

6 x 4 – Signed

Hannah Waterman is an English actress, daughter of Minder star Dennis Waterman and actress Patricia Maynard. She is best known for her role of Laura Beale on BBC soap Eastenders.

c/o EASTENDERS,
